<!-- Slot 3 · System board · Lightnote — the system as anatomy, not a specimen
     sheet. A fixed 1920x1080 canvas scaled to fit by the .ln-plate-canvas
     container transform (no JS), laid out atoms -> molecules -> organisms ->
     system. Every value verbatim from DESIGN_DNA.md; motion in the product's
